My days start early. My alarm rings at 7 o'clock and I wake up with the radio.

00:00:33.660 --> 00:00:45.360
Like most people, I stay a little bit of time in bed. And when I'm almost up, I take my phone to make sure of nothing had happened while I was sleeping and that requires my attention .

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:49.220
If it didn't happen, I stay at bed a little bit more.

00:00:51.640 --> 00:01:01.180
Now, it is time to start the day. First my body needs, is a good glass of water, something that is not necesary to say, is that it is good for the body.

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:07.160
After that, I get comfortable to read my favourite news sources to know everything before leaving bed.

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:11.360
And watch some videos of my favourite youtube channels.

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:19.060
Some stretching, and it is time to front facing the world out of bed.

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:32.480
In winter, I take showers at night. Because of that, I wash my face to wake up seriously, and then, I prepare sonmething for breakfast.

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:47.040
I take for breakfast toast with cheese spread, and a cup of tea. I love tea, and I almost never leave my house without having breakfast first.

00:01:47.620 --> 00:01:55.900
If the time lets me, I try to tahe a relaxed breakfast time, to keep reading, checking my social media, and charging energy for the day ahead.

00:01:56.840 --> 00:01:58.840
Now, activate!

