Lets start with my cleaning and makeup routine.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:14.840
First, untangle the mess made in my hair trough the night.

00:02:15.340 --> 00:02:17.340
And move it of my face.

00:02:20.460 --> 00:02:26.180
