00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:32.700
While the product does it's work, I wash my teeth as a good girl.

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:43.480
I rinse everything, and after drying, I apply a moisturizer creme. This one, is the one I showed you in my january's favourites (watch this video!)

